# Files to ignore during Render deployment
# Similar to .gitignore but for Render-specific ignores

# Development files
*.md
!README.md
!PRODUCTION_CHECKLIST.md

# Test files
**/*.test.js
**/*.spec.js
**/tests/
**/test/

# Documentation
docs/

# Editor files
.vscode/
.idea/

# Environment examples
**/.env.example

# Backups and temporary files
**/backups/
**/tmp/
**/temp/
